ockquote>正路就算無save, 你因為非正常途經close左個word ，你再開返word 佢會有個recover version 出現嫁wo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果無既話就無啦，無auto save 到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓豬就係話自己on99 save 左空白<br />\n<br />\n仲要reboot <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62507b973a367139615d1452d68d103fb26d163","tid":29080,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:35:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解而家仲有人會用 word 呢 d 垃圾打文 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有得睇字數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家仲有邊隻打文嘅軟件冇得睇字數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPages邊到有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"90bf95e7173c64acf400c7d248bf742ffe328d41","tid":29080,"uid":20792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:42:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有得睇字數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家仲有邊隻打文嘅軟件冇得睇字數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPages邊到有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係view -&gt;show word count<br />\n或者shift cmd W"},{"pid":"bae2ed932b136213dc583a1bb1b2c687930d2221","tid":29080,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:02:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家仲有邊隻打文嘅軟件冇得睇字數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPages邊到有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係view -&amp;gt;show word count<br />\n或者shift cmd W</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b594ef18e37425021b1ab56a89cb817167eec935","tid":29080,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:07:03.000Z","msg":"正常佢自動會有啲copy<br />\n 預防hang 機無哂資料<br />\n你睇下有冇"},{"pid":"b7be0b4cd34b15e58037d63c797e549cd1f73284","tid":29080,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:35:20.000Z","msg":"用 google docs 既 document  咪得<br />\n又可以係電話裝 app 執<br />\n<br />\n次次都有人用 microsoft office 係做野做功臨交之前<br />\n又死機，又死 os ，又死 file"},{"pid":"48264dd43d024823652435ae92e972cf02b45cfc","tid":29080,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:37:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解而家仲有人會用 word 呢 d 垃圾打文 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n裝Linux/OpenOffice?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果樓主真係裝linux+btrfs+snapper，頂多唔見一個鐘野<br />\n用dropbox/syncthing仲好，頂多唔見未save之前打既字</blockquote><br />\n而家可以自己 build libreoffice online <br />\n連 google 都唔信可以自己 build 個 dms 出黎"},{"pid":"4cb37b5ffe8a538612eb1a8f8586e862400f21f2","tid":29080,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPages邊到有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係view -&amp;amp;gt;show word count<br />\n或者shift cmd W</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問下有無得好似word咁逐個錯grammar 嘅字問你點執果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}